results.description:
Live Laugh Love Needle Minder

The most ironic of all sayings, with the most amazing tv character to ever appear.

Shown on a 3" embroidery hoop.

The needle minder comes with two magnets, one attached to the back, and one to hold it down onto your fabric from the back.
Simply chuck your needle down whenever you need to take a break and the magnet will hold it down for you.

To ensure that your magnets do not break, please slid them apart rather than pulling or slamming together. 
Given the nature of the magnets please take extra care around small children as these can become incredibly dangerous if swallowed.
